{"tid":2290578,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅冠聰 ：獎項屬於所有為民主自由奮鬥的香港人 「我們的抗爭，就成為了世界的抗爭」","createTime":"2020-11-18T06:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T07:14:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40f2ed4011e911db9053be58addffd44bc612b80","tid":2290578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"羅冠聰 ：獎項屬於所有為民主自由奮鬥的香港人<br />\n「我們的抗爭，就成為了世界的抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/5K6WVPSOTNGQDJQUESPY2WEYVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F5K6WVPSOTNGQDJQUESPY2WEYVE%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1QVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=0f3e26ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F5K6WVPSOTNGQDJQUESPY2WEYVE%2F&h=cb7e29a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/5K6WVPSOTNGQDJQUESPY2WEYVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰：代抗爭者領人權獎 <br />\n彭定康讚揚為民主勇敢抗共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_dP5BnyCdvLoXGMkH-HpohwCygE=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KVEVO6Q2UVB47OK2F5TDEMAYEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_dP5BnyCdvLoXGMkH-HpohwCygE%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKVEVO6Q2UVB47OK2F5TDEMAYEY.jpg&h=4bcdefc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■羅冠聰在網上發表得獎感受，提醒國際社會，不可讓極權坐大。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港步入極權時代，引起自由世界關注。身處英國倫敦的前香港眾志常委羅冠聰因積極推動香港民主，獲頒馬格尼茨基人權獎。羅冠聰表示，獎項是屬於所有爭取民主自由的香港人，呼籲全球捍衞香港和民主價值，勿讓極權主義有機可乘。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：俄會計揭政權貪腐慘死 促成制裁法案<br />\n<br />\n馬格尼茨基人權獎（Magnitsky Human Rights Awards）頒獎禮在網上舉行，表揚各國民權鬥士。前香港眾志常委兼前立法會議員羅冠聰獲頒「Outstanding Opposition Figure（傑出抗爭者）」獎項，羅冠聰致辭時表示，獲獎是對他推動民主運動的充份肯定，<span class=\"orange\">獎項屬於所有為民主自由奮鬥的香港人</span>，並提醒國際社會，香港的民主運動非常重要，非只為香港人，而是所有爭取民主自由的人，因香港處於極權與民主鬥爭的前沿，一旦失守，讓極權坐大，必定令民主價值遭受極大挫敗，不可讓極權政體所為欲為，<span class=\"orange\">「我們的抗爭，就成為了世界的抗爭」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4w1GxBrFyXRxzxU5AI7IvsI1Rvw=/1294x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MFWHS5BTYFB3LEHAT7ZU7HPNDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4w1GxBrFyXRxzxU5AI7IvsI1Rvw%3D%2F1294x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMFWHS5BTYFB3LEHAT7ZU7HPNDI.jpg&h=b9863076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭定康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱國安法打壓異見<br />\n<br />\n目前流亡倫敦的羅說，自己成長於貧窮家庭，父親在地盤工作，母親是清潔工人，童年時因家境貧困，只想長大後找好工作賺錢，讓父母過好生活，從未想過參與政治及社會運動，卻因看見香港社會問題叢生，政制崩壞，港人沒有選舉權，特首非一人一票普選誕生，只是由北京欽點，滿足極權需要，才投身社會運動，2014年雨傘運動時擔任學生領袖，2016年成為香港立法會史上最年輕議員，但翌年被北京取消議員資格，後更因雨傘運動入獄。<br />\n<br />\n羅指出，今年7月香港實施國安法後，北京可動輒以國家安全為由，羅織莫須有罪名，打壓異見，他因而決定出走英國，在國際社會上為香港發聲，推動民主自由，從事倡議工作，爭取各國強硬對待中俄等極權政體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「整個立法會被閹割」<br />\n<br />\n在網上頒獎的前港督彭定康致辭時讚揚羅冠聰是無懼中共打壓、勇敢捍衞香港民主、人權和法治的鬥士。羅冠聰曾為學生領袖，更成為最年輕的香港立法會議員，但被中共取消資格，現時整個立法會也被閹割。儘管如此，他仍一直努力為香港人爭取及捍衞民主、自由和人權，此乃香港成功的重要基石。<br />\n<br />\n頒獎禮主持則說，這是最難頒的獎項，<span class=\"orange\">因為有很多人均有參與香港的抗爭，可以獲得獎項</span>，<span class=\"red\">但當中不少人仍身在香港，擔心他們的名字與人權獎項公開扯上關係，對他們不利</span>。<br />\n<br />\n設立獎項的「全球馬格尼茨基司法運動」主管Bill Browder於twitter祝賀羅冠聰獲獎，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rWZyKG4kjrJFga51CjGBH5wdy-0=/1370x1555/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TDBIJFFKWZD33PJSV2SLDS5TUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrWZyKG4kjrJFga51CjGBH5wdy-0%3D%2F1370x1555%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTDBIJFFKWZD33PJSV2SLDS5TUA.jpg&h=d61e114b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce43a7ef62065e6f1aab60e135fcae925f99bd8a","tid":2290578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fd153bbb9582eb860fa537b23426de45260115","tid":2290578,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f1fff11db6a26b03421339aa2f583b4b924881","tid":2290578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce43a7ef62065e6f1aab60e135fcae925f99bd8a","tid":2290578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa